Half-Life 2 puzzle mod set in an Egyptian necropolis.


&quot;The game will not force you to fight hordes of mummies, or to solve all the puzzles. 
If you like
you can just wander around and break all the vases and such, through the entire game till the credits starts to roll: that's the easiest setting. 
But if you looking for action, just push a button here and there..and see what'll happen.&quot;
